Titulo: Reverse micelle synthesis of perovskite oxide nanoparticles

Sentencas: La0.6Sr0.4Cu0.2Fe0.8O3-delta, Ba(0.5)Sr0.4Co(0.8)Fe(0.2)O(3-delta) and LaFeO3-delta nanoparticles were synthesized by a reverse micelle procedure.
Titulo: Reverse micelle synthesis of perovskite oxide nanoparticles

Sentencas: Controlling the size of the micelles through the water:oil phase ratio enabled synthesis of phase pure perovskite particles with average sizes from 14 nm to 50 nm.
Titulo: Reverse micelle synthesis of perovskite oxide nanoparticles

Sentencas: Small amounts of an impurity phase, likely cobalt oxide, were detected in the XRD spectrum of high cobalt content samples of LSCF (x = 0.8).
Titulo: Reverse micelle synthesis of perovskite oxide nanoparticles

Sentencas: La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta nanoparticles were utilized to coat the surface of a dense thin-film La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta solid oxide fuel cell cathode.
Titulo: Reverse micelle synthesis of perovskite oxide nanoparticles

Sentencas: The polarization resistance of the nanoparticle coated electrode, measured at open circuit in air at 973 K, was 20% lower than an equivalent un-coated electrode.
Titulo: Reverse micelle synthesis of perovskite oxide nanoparticles
